      "writtenOn": "2020-08-05T05:53:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The realm check will replace \"access to the project\" check. Pass `true` as ExpectedResult to HasPermissionDryRun. It still will be valuable since the call will log projects that don\u0027t have realms.cfg yet (which is most of them). For them HasPermission(...) will be false, which is !\u003d true.\n\n\u003e Also, what to do with the project-scoped permission check?\n\nWhat do you mean by \"project-scoped permission check\"?",
